  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Monsters and Weapons</h2>A strategic rogue-like based on decision making. Fight your way through different areas, buy items and defeat the final boss to proclaim victory!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861940/extras/0ed7f857a65b0a2e71fede50be0cffb2.avif?t=1661756721\" width=690 height=70 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Highly strategic.<br><br></li><li> Unique \"semi\" turn-based fights where you control the pace.<br><br></li><li> Ten unlockable and unique classes.<br><br></li><li> Achievements (hard).<br><br></li><li> Impactful decisions with a smidge of luck.<br><br></li><li> Unlock Legendary Mode for the ultimate challenge!<br><br></li><li> Inventory management.<br><br></li><li> Boss fights.<br><br></li><li> Many items and creative item combinations.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861940/extras/882cc749de026b7c562e00ddc73e57c0.webp?t=1661756721\" width=750 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861940/extras/16a824ea88983cdfe8501e319bed3159.poster.avif?t=1661756721\" width=494 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861940/extras/16a824ea88983cdfe8501e319bed3159.webm?t=1661756721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861940/extras/16a824ea88983cdfe8501e319bed3159.mp4?t=1661756721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1861940/extras/434895ae72b1166f2b41801566c60632.webp?t=1661756721\" width=750 height=50 /